Headline: China counters Biden's Covid origins Wuhan lab probe ... by calling for a US lab probe - CNN
Text: By Nectar Gan and Jessie Yeung, CNNUpdated 0940 GMT (1740 HKT) May 28, 2021 Hong Kong (CNN)US President Joe Biden's call for a renewed investigation into the origins of the coronavirus feels like déjà vu in Beijing.
